    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Landforms smaller than a continent, completely surrounded by water at high water. Islands appear in oceans, seas, lakes, or rivers. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
